snippet.title: Pulsar ][ Disk Drive sound (Apple II - Sirius)
snippet.description:
Pulsar ][ (https://www.mobygames.com/game/pulsar-ii_) was an action game published by Sirius software in 1981 for the Apple ][. The copy protection used half tracks from track 1A.5 to 1D.5 and you can hear interesting sounds from using those tracks in the boot sequence.

Credits:
Disk image - 4AM
